{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-11",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_11_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 11 - Gutman",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 4,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 728.32,
  "page_end_sec": 976.16,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.658,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 728.32,
      "end": 728.76,
      "text": "Don't we all?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 729.18,
      "end": 731.42,
      "text": "I don't trust a man that says he's not."
    },
    {
      "start": 732.6,
      "end": 735.24,
      "text": "And the man that's telling the truth when he says he's not,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 735.32,
      "end": 736.86,
      "text": "I distrust most of all,"
    },
    {
      "start": 736.96,
      "end": 738.76,
      "text": "because he's an ass,"
    },
    {
      "start": 739.28,
      "end": 742.208,
      "text": "and an ass that's going contrary to the laws of nature.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 743.552,
      "end": 744.68,
      "text": "Spade exhaled smoke.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 745.28,
      "end": 746.8,
      "text": "His face was politely attentive."
    },
    {
      "start": 747.5,
      "end": 747.8,
      "text": "He said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 748.76,
      "end": 749.08,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 749.18,
      "end": 751.69,
      "text": "Now let's talk about the blackbird.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 752.74,
      "end": 755.04,
      "text": "The fat man smiled benevolently at Spade.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 755.77,
      "end": 756.52,
      "text": "Let's,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 756.52,
      "end": 757.12,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 758.02,
      "end": 760.58,
      "text": "He squinted so that fat puffs crowding together",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 760.58,
      "end": 762.76,
      "text": "left nothing visible of his eyes except a"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.76,
      "end": 763.42,
      "text": "dark gleam."
    },
    {
      "start": 764.46,
      "end": 765.06,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 765.16,
      "end": 765.6,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 765.81,
      "end": 768.02,
      "text": "have you any conception of how much"
    },
    {
      "start": 768.02,
      "end": 769.99,
      "text": "money can be made out of that blackbird?"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.96,
      "end": 771.2,
      "text": "No.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 772.76,
      "end": 776.02,
      "text": "The fat man leaned forward and put a bloated pink hand on the arm of",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 776.08,
      "end": 776.66,
      "text": "Spade's chair."
    },
    {
      "start": 777.6,
      "end": 778.24,
      "text": "\"'Well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 778.34,
      "end": 778.58,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 778.78,
      "end": 780.12,
      "text": "if I told you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 780.68,
      "end": 781.7,
      "text": "if I told you half,"
    },
    {
      "start": 781.98,
      "end": 783.35,
      "text": "you'd call me a liar.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 784.544,
      "end": 785.22,
      "text": "Spade smiled.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 786.15,
      "end": 787.26,
      "text": "\"'No,' he said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 787.78,
      "end": 788.96,
      "text": "\"'Not even if I thought it."
    },
    {
      "start": 790.02,
      "end": 791.74,
      "text": "But if you don't want to take the risk,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 791.88,
      "end": 793.52,
      "text": "just tell me what it is and"
    },
    {
      "start": 793.52,
      "end": 794.84,
      "text": "I'll figure out the profit.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 795.38,
      "end": 796.84,
      "text": "The fat man laughed."
    },
    {
      "start": 797.5,
      "end": 798.2,
      "text": "\"'You couldn't.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 798.66,
      "end": 799.4,
      "text": "You couldn't do it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 799.44,
      "end": 799.62,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 800.86,
      "end": 802.74,
      "text": "could do it that hadn't had a world of",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 802.74,
      "end": 804.4,
      "text": "experience with things of that sort,"
    },
    {
      "start": 804.56,
      "end": 806.68,
      "text": "and—he paused"
    },
    {
      "start": 807.54,
      "end": 810.06,
      "text": "impressively—there aren't any other things of that sort.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 810.92,
      "end": 813.74,
      "text": "His bulbs jostled one another as he laughed again.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 814.1,
      "end": 815.84,
      "text": "He stopped laughing abruptly."
    },
    {
      "start": 816.92,
      "end": 817.4,
      "text": "His fleshy",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 817.44,
      "end": 820.02,
      "text": "lips hung a little apart as laughter had left them."
    },
    {
      "start": 820.768,
      "end": 822.76,
      "text": "He stared at Spade with an intentness",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 822.76,
      "end": 824.08,
      "text": "that suggested myopia."
    },
    {
      "start": 825.14,
      "end": 825.46,
      "text": "He asked,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 826.56,
      "end": 828.736,
      "text": "\"'You mean you don't know what it is?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 829.728,
      "end": 831.92,
      "text": "Amazement took the throatiness out of his voice.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 832.96,
      "end": 834.96,
      "text": "Spade made a careless gesture with his cigar.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 836.25,
      "end": 836.8,
      "text": "\"'Oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 836.8,
      "end": 838.14,
      "text": "hell,' he said lightly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 838.31,
      "end": 840.24,
      "text": "\"'I know what it's supposed to look like."
    },
    {
      "start": 840.4,
      "end": 841.98,
      "text": "I know the value in life"
    },
    {
      "start": 841.98,
      "end": 843.48,
      "text": "and money you people put on it."
    },
    {
      "start": 844.14,
      "end": 845.32,
      "text": "I don't know what it is.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 846.56,
      "end": 847.552,
      "text": "\"'She didn't tell you?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 848.512,
      "end": 849.36,
      "text": "\"'Miss O'Shaughnessy?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 849.56,
      "end": 850.4,
      "text": "\"'Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 850.76,
      "end": 851.56,
      "text": "A lovely girl,"
    },
    {
      "start": 851.66,
      "end": 852.12,
      "text": "sir.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 853.056,
      "end": 853.3,
      "text": "\"'Uh-huh.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 853.36,
      "end": 853.71,
      "text": "No.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 854.68,
      "end": 859.14,
      "text": "The fat man's eyes were dark gleams in ambush behind pink puffs of",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 859.26,
      "end": 859.4,
      "text": "flesh."
    },
    {
      "start": 860.58,
      "end": 861.8,
      "text": "He said indistinctly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 862.88,
      "end": 863.86,
      "text": "She must know.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 864.7,
      "end": 865.04,
      "text": "And then,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 865.84,
      "end": 867.04,
      "text": "And Cairo didn't either?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 868.352,
      "end": 869.32,
      "text": "Cairo is cagey.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 869.75,
      "end": 871.14,
      "text": "He's willing to buy it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 871.2,
      "end": 872.6,
      "text": "but he won't risk telling me"
    },
    {
      "start": 872.66,
      "end": 873.8,
      "text": "anything I don't know already."
    },
    {
      "start": 874.78,
      "end": 877.16,
      "text": "The fat man moistened his lips with his tongue.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 878.74,
      "end": 880.5,
      "text": "How much is he willing to buy it for?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 881.2,
      "end": 881.6,
      "text": "he asked.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 882.4,
      "end": 883.24,
      "text": "Ten thousand dollars.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 884.1,
      "end": 886.02,
      "text": "The fat man laughed scornfully.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 886.6,
      "end": 887.28,
      "text": "Ten thousand!"
    },
    {
      "start": 887.62,
      "end": 888.46,
      "text": "And dollars,"
    },
    {
      "start": 888.54,
      "end": 888.98,
      "text": "mind you!"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.34,
      "end": 890.12,
      "text": "Not even pounds!"
    },
    {
      "start": 891.296,
      "end": 892.36,
      "text": "That's the Greek for you.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 892.96,
      "end": 893.3,
      "text": "Humph!"
    },
    {
      "start": 894.26,
      "end": 895.32,
      "text": "And what did you say to that?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 896.26,
      "end": 897.12,
      "text": "I said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 897.24,
      "end": 898.72,
      "text": "if I turned it over to him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 898.78,
      "end": 900.22,
      "text": "I'd expect the ten thousand."
    },
    {
      "start": 901.38,
      "end": 901.68,
      "text": "Ah,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 901.72,
      "end": 902.12,
      "text": "yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 902.36,
      "end": 902.8,
      "text": "if."
    },
    {
      "start": 903.616,
      "end": 904.36,
      "text": "Nicely put,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 904.52,
      "end": 904.68,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 905.34,
      "end": 908.82,
      "text": "The fat man's forehead squirmed in a flesh-blurred frown.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 909.88,
      "end": 911.42,
      "text": "They must know,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 911.68,
      "end": 912.84,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 912.9,
      "end": 913.84,
      "text": "only partly aloud."
    },
    {
      "start": 914.2,
      "end": 914.3,
      "text": "then,"
    },
    {
      "start": 914.74,
      "end": 915.68,
      "text": "do they?"
    },
    {
      "start": 916.608,
      "end": 918.26,
      "text": "Do they know what the bird is,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 918.38,
      "end": 918.54,
      "text": "sir?"
    },
    {
      "start": 919.3,
      "end": 920.21,
      "text": "What is your impression?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 921.9,
      "end": 924.12,
      "text": "\"'I can't help you there,' Spade confessed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 924.75,
      "end": 926.12,
      "text": "\"'There's not much to go by."
    },
    {
      "start": 927.264,
      "end": 928.42,
      "text": "Cairo didn't say he did,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 928.6,
      "end": 929.98,
      "text": "and he didn't say he didn't."
    },
    {
      "start": 930.7,
      "end": 931.76,
      "text": "She said she didn't,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 931.76,
      "end": 932.78,
      "text": "but I took it for"
    },
    {
      "start": 932.84,
      "end": 934.43,
      "text": "granted that she was lying.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 935.64,
      "end": 937.68,
      "text": "\"'That was not an injudicious thing to do,'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 937.78,
      "end": 938.048,
      "text": "too,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 938.56,
      "end": 939.4,
      "text": "the fat man said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 940.1,
      "end": 942.34,
      "text": "but his mind was obviously not on his words.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 942.84,
      "end": 944.42,
      "text": "He scratched his head."
    },
    {
      "start": 944.77,
      "end": 947.46,
      "text": "He frowned until his forehead was marked by raw"
    },
    {
      "start": 947.6,
      "end": 948.2,
      "text": "red creases."
    },
    {
      "start": 949.2,
      "end": 952.36,
      "text": "He fidgeted in his chair as much as its size and his size",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 952.46,
      "end": 953.26,
      "text": "permitted fidgeting."
    },
    {
      "start": 953.81,
      "end": 955.24,
      "text": "He shut his eyes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 955.42,
      "end": 956.58,
      "text": "suddenly opened them wide,"
    },
    {
      "start": 956.74,
      "end": 956.98,
      "text": "and"
    },
    {
      "start": 957.06,
      "end": 957.62,
      "text": "said to Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 958.54,
      "end": 959.48,
      "text": "\"'Maybe they don't.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 960.56,
      "end": 963.98,
      "text": "His bulbous pink face slowly lost its worried frown and then,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 964.04,
      "end": 964.26,
      "text": "more"
    },
    {
      "start": 964.8,
      "end": 967.38,
      "text": "took on an expression of ineffable happiness."
    },
    {
      "start": 968.52,
      "end": 970.24,
      "text": "\"'If they don't,' he cried,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 970.42,
      "end": 970.82,
      "text": "and again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 971.488,
      "end": 972.02,
      "text": "\"'if they don't,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 972.16,
      "end": 976.16,
      "text": "I'm the only one in the whole white sweet world who does!'"
    }
  ]
}